-fPIC is needed by bzip2, and by libgd

CXXFLAGS and LDFLAGS need to have /usr/local for giac's use of libintl
(i.e. LDFLAGS="-L/usr/local/lib" CXXFLAGS="-I/usr/local/include"

CXXFLAGS must not be empty for flint (some bug there)

careful with setting CFLAGS to "-I/usr/local/include" - this breaks ecm build
(it pulls in the wrong GMP header then)
