flang - specific (in particular needed for openblas and scipy (I guess numpy etc. too))

./configure FC=flang

FFLAGS="-I/usr/local/flang/include"
LDFLAGS="$LDFLAGS -lexecinfo -lm"

one needs to create a fake libgfortran.so, to let scipy link against it without an error;
e.g. make a link  $SAGE_LOCAL/lib/libgfortran.so pointing to system's libm.so
